<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Skewer (Q)</b></li><ul><li> This ability will now cast slightly faster to be more in line with the animation.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 27 (March 17, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Grievous Wounds (W)</li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where the magical damage done by this ability would not proc generic non-basic/non-ability specific damage triggers, such as Judgement's Magic Shred or Will Thief's Magic Resistance steal.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Skewer (Q)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 950, from previous value of 1000.</li></ul><li>Jagged Volley (E)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 11%.</li></ul><li>Splinter Spines (R)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 500, from previous value of 550.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 23 (Jan 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Jagged Volley (E)</B></li><ul><li>The slow applied by this ability has been increased to 30/35/40/45/50%, up from 20/25/30/35/40%.</li></ul><li><B>Splintering Spines (R)</B></li><ul><li>This ability now grants Vex 20% increased basic attack range for the duration of the ability.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 17 (November 7, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Jagged Volley (E)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 12/11/10/9/8, down from 14/13/12/11/10.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 16 (Oct 31, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug that was causing visuals to hitch slightly when using Jagged Volley (E).</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 15 (October 22, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Recommended items have been updated.</li><li><B>Grievous Wounds (W)</B></li><ul><li>The base percentage max health damage of this ability has been increased to 3/3.5/4/4.5/5%, up from 2/2.5/3/3.5/4%.</li><li>The duration of this ability when activated has been increased to 8 seconds, up from 7.</li></ul><li><B>Jagged Volley (E)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 14/13/12/11/10 seconds, down from 18/16/15/12/10.</li></ul><li><B>Splintering Spines (R)</B></li><ul><li>The tooltip for this ability has been updated to show the exact amount of damage the splash of this ability will do, rather than displaying it only as a percentage of your attack damage.</li><li>The duration of this ability when activated has been increased to 8 seconds, up from 7.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 14 (October 16, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Updated ability icons for Vex.</li></ul>